                "href": "/profile/Wes-Kretzer"
            },
            "answer_text": "The enemy of DVD\u2019s is age and handling. They can be played thousands of times with minimal degradation, but the oil from your hands and aging (I\u2019m talking more than 10 years) is actually the issue. The heads don\u2019t touch the DVD, they merely read the contents, so playing the DVD does not degrade the recording at all. ",
